Use either
pylupdate5 ../cwsim.py ../mplwidget.py ../cwsimgui.ui -ts xx_XX.ts
or
pylupdate6 ../cwsim.py ../mplwidget.py ../cwsimgui.ui -ts xx_XX.ts
where xx is the language and XX the country

Then use
linguist xx_XX.ts
to edit the translation file. Once satisfied make the release file
lrelease xx_XX.ts -qm xx_XX.qm
to get the compressed translation file used by cwsim.py
